Passive Ability

Reduces the duration of debuffs inflicted on this Pokémon.

Attack

Auto Attack

Becomes boosted attacks when the boosted attack gauge is full, dealing increased damage in an area of effect centered on the opposing Pokémon they hit.

Each time the user deals damage to opposing Pokémon, the boosted attack gauge increases by 1, becoming full when the user deals damage 8 times. After not dealing damage for 3s, the boosted attack gauge decreases by 2 every 0.5s.

Astonish

Move 1

7.00s Ranged

Lets out a sound blast in a forward direction. The shout explodes when it hits an enemy or after traveling a set distance, dealing damage in an area and decreasing enemy movement speed by 30% for 2s.

122% Atk + 16 x (Level - 1) + 290

Astonish Upgrade Choices

Dragon Breath

7.50s Ranged

Exhales a mighty gust in the designated direction, dealing damage to enemies in the area-of-effect and decreasing their movement speed by 30% for 2s. The gust also leaves the ground burning for 3s. Enemies in this area take damage-over-time and have their movement speed decreased for a short time. If this move is used while the user is flying with Dragon Dance, the mighty gust is exhaled along Dragon Dance's flight path, dealing damage to enemies in the area and decreasing their movement speed for a short time.

60% Atk + 4 x (Level - 1) + 160

30% Atk + 2 x (Level - 1) + 80

Deals increased damage and increases the slow to 45% for 2s.

66% Atk + 4 x (Level - 1) + 176

33% Atk + 2 x (Level - 1) + 88

Shadow Ball

7.50s Ranged

The user hurls a shadowy blob in the designated direction, damaging opposing Pokémon hit and applying a marker with 4 parts to them for 5s; then dashes in the chosen direction forward. When the user hits a marked target, one part of the marker is consumed to deal additional damage. The fourth part of the mark deals increased additional damage and removes the mark when consumed, and the user restores 15% max HP.

110% Atk + 5 x (Level - 1) + 265

22% Atk + 1 x (Level - 1) + 53

Increases the damage of this move and the additional damage from marks.

Quick Attack

Move 2

8.00s Dash

Dashes in the designated direction, increasing basic attack speed by 40% for 2s.

Quick Attack Upgrade Choices

Dragon Dance

11.00s Dash

The user prepares a circular flight path in the designated direction, then moves into a direction either side to fly on the path; the flight path takes 3.5s to complete. While flying, the user increases their basic attack speed by 200% and they continuously use auto attacks, dealing 10% reduced damage to opposing Pokémon hit. If this move is used again while the user is flying, the user stops flying, becomes briefly invincible and dashes a short distance forward. If the user knocks out a Pokémon from the opposing team, this move's cooldown is reset. If the user assists in knocking out a Pokémon from the opposing team instead, this move's cooldown is reduced by 50%.

When this move is used, Dragon Breath's cooldown is reset.

90% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

103.5% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

While the user is flying, auto attacks restore the user's HP for an additional 25% of damage dealt.

Phantom Force

12.00s Buff

The user enters stealth for up to 6s or until using an attack, increasing their movement speed by 30% and increasing the boosted basic attack gauge by 1 every 1s. When the user exits stealth, the user's basic attack speed is increased by 85% for 3s.

When this move is learned, if the user knocks out a Pokémon from the opposing team, this move's cooldown is reset and the user's Attack is increased by 8 until the end of the battle (up to 10 times; maximum 80 bonus Attack).

Reduces this move's cooldown by 0.5s per opposing Pokémon hit by the user's auto attacks.

Dreep and Destroy

Unite Move

10s Ranged

Unlocks at level 9

The user launches two Dreepy at up to 2 different opposing Pokémon in range, damaging them and dealing additional missing HP damage to each target. If there is only one target in range, the second Dreepy deals 30% of the full damage to the target. A maximum of 2 uses can be kept in reserve for this Unite Move; there is a 2s cooldown between uses for this move.

Against wild Pokémon: additional missing HP damage is capped at 1200.

Also deals 10% of enemy missing HP.
101% Atk + 4 x (Level - 1) + 180

Unite Buffs (3s duration):

10% Max HP Shield, 10% Movement Speed for 3s; Has an internal cooldown of 30s to activate Energy Amplifier; Has an internal cooldown of 60s to activate Buddy Barrier;
